title: 'Indo western palazzo'
body: I purchased these for 199, MRP is 1199 which is 83.4% discount. It's written 100% cotton. Cloth is soft. Print, colour and design are nice and attractive. It would have been better if there were pockets. Price tag was folded, had creases. It was attached with thread and not plastic like other tags. It has loops on both sides for hanging. Finishing could be better. It's written as pyjama bottom but they look like palazzo.
